                  <dt>Descriptions</dt>
          <dd>
            <dl>
                              <dt>Description</dt>
                <dd>This sheet forms part of a seventeenth-century Dutch album, in its original binding, which contains 41 small, full-page drawings on parchment by more than 27 different artists.</dd>
                                                       </dl>
          </dd>
        
